|                                  |                                                |
| :------------------------------: | :--------------------------------------------: |
|         `PandaReach-v1`          |                 `PandaPush-v1`                 |
| ![PandaReach-v1](docs/reach.gif) |         ![PandaPush-v1](docs/push.gif)         |
|         `PandaSlide-v1`          |             `PandaPickAndPlace-v1`             |
